 *Snow Tech and Shadow Cat saw the female bot that
called herself "Dracona" Put away her gun and they
sighed with relief. The last thing they wanted was to
start something. Ramulas Had told them this was
prehistoric earth, and was going to show them there
lodgings when a blast rattled the ship, and He left
them with Dracona. They were confused. Snow Tech
turned to Dracona,*

 " Does every one come and go this way?" 

 * A sudden screech distracted the bots once more as a
female raptor/bot ran down the hall, followed by an
exact copy, but male. As the male bot walked by,
Shadow Cat tilted her head and stared at him,*

 " Nice tail." *she breathed, to no one in
particular.*

 * Snow Tech Smiled to his sister, as she watched the
bot pass,*

 " Jezze, and you said i wuz bad!"

 * Shadow Cat glared at him, and made a rude gesture
at him. She composed herself and kicked him in the
shin when he began to snicker. She looked at Dracona
and said,*

 " of all the sparks in the universe i had to get the
dumbest ass-hole for a brother. and, giving Snow Tech
an extra mean glare, started to walk after Dinobot.
Snow Tech giggled and followed, winking at Dracona.*
